{
  "stem": "6878.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We always went to shul day and night, and we always pray to you, and we are honest people, and why are you punishing, and so on and so on and so.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we carried on like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't help it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And day by day, we laid there a hundred days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by the end of the hundred days, the Germans were pushed quite far, to Lithuania-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] through Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And German communication, telephone communication, moved in into our house where we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just to take me back?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I can-- sorry I didn't include that to start off with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the ghetto, I was-- I registered myself to go and work on the airport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, by going through the gate, we used to register ourselves that we're going through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we used to walk up, I'd say, about not even half a kilometer, when the road curved, I used to just take off my stars and go out on the pavement with all the training people and go into town and spend the day.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had some friends, Lithuanian friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them even offered me a passport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to them, yes, I'll accept a passport, but I want two or nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want a passport for Ida, also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Obviously, it was nothing, because they couldn't get for Ida a passport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they say that this one was shot, and this one was killed, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We've got our passport, and we'll put on your picture and so on, and it'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I didn't agree on this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I've got a passport to leave amongst Lithuanian, Lithuanian passports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I used to go out like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one day, I went into a caretaker's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
